WEBVTT

1
00:44:51.890 --> 00:44:53.980 
你们想倒打一耙吗
Are you trying to turn this around on me?

2
00:44:53.980 --> 00:44:55.410 
这还不止  奥林
That's not all, Orrin.

3
00:44:55.450 --> 00:44:56.450 
还有你的地役权为了使用自己土地的便利而使用他人土地的权利
Your easement.

4
00:44:56.450 --> 00:44:58.730 
你看  山麓电网每隔几年
You see, every couple of years the Piedmont Electric,

5
00:44:58.730 --> 00:45:01.010 
就申请让输电线横穿加夫尼
they apply to bring power lines through Gaffney.

6
00:45:01.010 --> 00:45:02.950 
你这块地正好在路线之上
The route comes right through your lot.

7
00:45:02.950 --> 00:45:04.170 
我和吉恩每次都把这事压下
Now, Gene and I always fight them off.

8
00:45:04.170 --> 00:45:06.900 
但今年  他们要是再来申请
But this year, if they were to reapply, hmm...

9
00:45:06.900 --> 00:45:08.030 
政府强制征收
Eminent domain.

10
00:45:08.030 --> 00:45:11.130 
拆掉这么漂亮的房子  真是可惜
It would be such a shame to have to tear down this beautiful home.

11
00:45:11.340 --> 00:45:12.600 
见鬼去吧  弗兰克
Fuck you, Frank.

12
00:45:13.100 --> 00:45:15.990 
你休想跑到我家来  还一副你的地盘的样子
You can't just roll up on my property and act like you own it.

13
00:45:21.850 --> 00:45:23.520 
不  我可以
Oh, but I can.

